<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="M" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Mental" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Mental,</orth> pertaining to the mind, intellectual: <cit><quote>the still and m. parts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 1.3.200" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. I, 3, 200</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>'twixt his m. and his active parts,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 2.3.184" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>what a m. power this eye shoots forth!</quote> <bibl n="shak. tim 1.1.31" default="NO" valid="yes">Tim. I, 1, 31</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>